msgid ""
"Single press to display the context menu, double press to write "
"[Grave](keyEquiv_en.html#aboveTab) or "
"Shift+[Grave](keyEquiv_en.html#aboveTab) or their replacements: this option "
"allows you to display the context menu by pressing the "
"[Grave](keyEquiv_en.html#aboveTab) key which will be more practical if you "
"very rarely type the characters [Grave](keyEquiv_en.html#aboveTab) and "
"Shift+[Grave](keyEquiv_en.html#aboveTab);"
