"Back up the current configuration s: Copies the add-on's .ini file to a "
".inibak file."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"Restore Saved Configuration r: Copies the .inibak file to the .ini and "
"reloads the settings;"
